title: Video Quality for Rendering
useCurrentDesc: Render with the video currently playing in the preview ({{quality}})
redownloadFullDesc: Download the video again in the highest available quality for better rendering results
redownloadQualityDesc: Download the video again in a different quality for rendering
cookieSupportTooltip: Uses browser cookies for authentication to access higher quality videos and bypass login restrictions
cookieDisabledTooltip: Browser cookies are disabled. Downloads will be faster but may have limited quality options and fail on restricted content.
